webserver
=========

Install and configure Apache 2.4 and set up some VirtualHosts.


Role variables
==============

webserver_sites
---------------

List of sites to configure on Apache.

  sitename: <string>
  servername: <fqdn>
  serveraliases:
    - <fqdn>
    - ...
  serveradmin: <default: webserver_serveradmin>
  install_wordpress: <bool, default: no>


webserver_serveradmin
---------------------

Default: webmaster@localhost
(Change it!)
